等知名互联网企业或研究院，以及中科院、研究所、信息工程研究所等国内著名科研所及清华、北大、浙大等国内知名高校继续深造学习。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-align: center;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100009212" data-ratio="0.4125" data-type="jpeg" data-w="720" style="outline: 0px;vertical-align: inherit;border-radius: 8px;line-height: 27.2px;background-size: 16px !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 433px !important;height: auto !important;" title="··.jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/p0EKKqIpcE4wKu07ssYfibeDx9oTYgBMnS1Le4CXeTbCg6HYtEJvzbeWMJolWO2WMTwTAgxPevaaKHpHnO5upbQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p mp-original-font-size="17" mp-original-line-height="27.200000762939453" style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-align: center;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 27.2px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100009214" data-ratio="0.34629629629629627" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;vertical-align: inherit;border-radius: 8px;line-height: 27.2px;background-size: 16px !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 427px !important;height: auto !important;" title="222.jpeg" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/p0EKKqIpcE4wKu07ssYfibeDx9oTYgBMnbheiboINx1FQKxx9zseZGoQfkJelcZSZFvDZdzZLx4NU9m6XvNpB31w/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br><span style="font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;">扫码添加课程顾问，备注&nbsp;“咨询课程”</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100022414" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="400" style="width: 59%;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/VyxCxUCalFOU0Fz371cnoY1uHzWfaxsf8WZLeqoVmHlGy00bw7ibia0nrMAribciaLTyzHNRjGXcewD0JK0iaH0b2IQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, system-ui, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: 微软雅黑, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">锁定入学名额</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p>]]></summary>
