        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<div data-role="outer" label="edit by 135editor" style="margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);visibility: visible;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><div data-role="paragraph" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><h1 style="margin-right: 5px;margin-left: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">随着国家计算机与软件技术的发展，每年报名参加计算机软件资格考试</span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">（简称：软考）</span></strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">的人越来越多。</span></span></h1><p style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;"><br></p><h1 style="margin-right: 5px;margin-left: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">据工信部新闻发布会消息：</span></h1><p style="margin-right: 5px;margin-left: 5px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><br></p><h1 style="margin-right: 5px;margin-le