;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">据悉，国内</span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">持软考证书的IT人才缺口高达950万</span></strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">，持软考证书的全职IT人才平均年薪可达</span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">20-50万元。</span></strong></span></span></p></div><p style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;"><br></p><div style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin-right: 5px;margin-left: 5px;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">前几天，软考官方公布了24年软考大改革，</span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);visibility: visible;"><strong style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;">即技术类科目变多了！</span></strong></span></p></div><p style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;"><br></p><div style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-right: 5px;margin-left: 5px;outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">这意味着，</span><span style="outline: 0px;text-decoration: underline;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">市场急需持有软考证书的IT人才，且今年改革第一年，难度不会提升。</span></strong></span></p></div><p style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;"><br></p><div data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="89056" style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;"><p style="outline: 0px;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">这对所有准备今年报考的程序员来说都是重大利好！</span></strong></span></p></div><div data-role="paragraph" style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;"><div style="outline: 0px;vertical-align: inherit;line-height: 1.5em;"><p style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-family: H