        <title type="html"><![CDATA[150 位，我们出成绩了！]]></title>
        <id>2247505895_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NjUxMzg5MA==&amp;mid=2247505895&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ea3e85ca3b198f7f734a63348ecefb75&amp;chksm=cf9a1e6af8ed977ce57d2a07d55619c3c2c75969f7bd692d563d0b015266b1c8a1e5087c328c#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-03-30T04:26:24.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<div data-tool="mdnice编辑器" data-website="https://www.mdnice.com" style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">大家好，我是小北。</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">我跟知名编程博主 小林coding 合伙后端训练营已经快半年了，这是一个帮助同学们解决面试突击痛点的训练营。</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;">我已经持续参与、观察训练营大半年了，我觉得非常靠谱，早期推荐了几个比较有需求的同学参加，目前回访了几次，基本都很满意，有人带着做项目、复习，比自己高效很多，随时有导师解答各种技术、非技术的问题：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100022243" data-ratio="1.2092592592592593" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="width: 260px;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/VyxCxUCalFPmm38N7UvVibgPvyoPaicLxXCVYmib8LK9BmnrFnvGrfncCU8g0WY7HQzm3CXdy7NODul07icXp2R6jQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;"><br></span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">所以今天在公众号给有需要的同学介绍一下训练营～</span><br></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">大家可以先思考下自己找工作遇到的最大困难是什么？</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">比如：</span></p><ul data-tool="mdnice编辑器" class="list-paddingleft-1" style="margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;visibility: visible;"><li style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;">没有系统的计划和复习路线，效率很低</p></li><li style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;">感觉学知识很难，坚持不下去，时常感到焦虑</p></li><li style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;">缺少专业的知识讲解，很多技术只是一知半解，八股背了就忘</p></li><li style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;">缺少有竞争力的项目</p></li><li style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><p style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;">没有面试机会，也不知道自己水平如何</p></li></ul><p style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">我们也是针对这些大家最常遇到的困难，设定了一条龙的求职服务。</span></p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;visibility: visible;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022208" data-ratio="0.34629629629629627" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible !important;width: 656.984px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/mngWTkJEOYLicdoY1lyzzKLib3s5LJ9zYTJK1YbA0DM4H3IdnfMTbBlgZfC3bdCVx4ibt9EYCJd4Uiac7ArmQ8unZQ/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></figure><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;visibility: visible;">训练营从创立到现在已经有一年多了，服务越来越到位、内容越来越完善，相应的也出了非常多的成果，基本上每天都有学员主动跟我们报喜。</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding-top: 1em;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022207" data-ratio