ce编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">计划通常是以专项的方式推进，比如第一个周期，学习Redis（通常是2-3周，学习的内容由训练营提供），然后紧接着是专项题库的练习题，需要你们自己作答，然后我们会帮你找出不到位的地方，还会提供给你大厂面试官遇到这些问题，会怎么分析和回答，再花一周review和加强，然后继续攻坚下个专项，以此迭代，学完所有专项之后会进行简历打磨和模拟面试。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100022215" data-ratio="1.6408977556109725" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="802" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/HQKXnkPzzdsEZuLYzVrIUQfl5jP9wnOgkCibGPYhLJPUksNLHA0Kj17ZDKo5DR9ldYPW9EDPxCbzS4IbR1fceGw/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">以上就是整体流程，下面会详细介绍我们到底有哪些价值，提供哪些服务。</span></p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"></figure><h2 data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 30px;margin-bottom: 15px;outline: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.3em;color: black;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(65, 105, 225);"><span style="margin-right: 3px;padding: 3px 10px 1px;outline: 0px;display: inline-block;background: rgb(65, 105, 225);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-top-right-radius: 3px;border-top-left-radius: 3px;">&nbsp;训练营提供哪些价值</span></h2><h3 data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 15px;outline: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 20px;color: black;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(65, 105, 225);">1. 求职服务一条龙</span></h3><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">如果你感觉学习效率低，入营后我们就给你 1 V 1 定制学习计划，我们有原创的技术学习和面试题库，按照顺序学就行了~</span></p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022220" data-ratio="0.5018518518518519" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 25px;margin-left: auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8SEntvTMicPlHq2ElCw0Hia8cgqDosquSEj1a3rbHnqTIKWkrA1DiaOd1aQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></figure><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">如果你感觉学不下去，每周我们会跟进你的周报，解决你学习遇到的困难，大大增加你的学习动力。</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022217" data-ratio="0.475" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 637px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8So9Q8oRvnjSGX3uuW6f65wEcwk1YlPfbichGD8NyLga1EBtBYykd6LqQ/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">如果你不知道如何写一份能打的简历，<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.32px;">我们有 1 对 1 的简历修改，帮你进行优化和打磨，</span></span><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">比如这位同学，之前自己写的简历，投了很多岗位，都没有面试机会，被我们修改之后，获得了很多机会，并且还进了大厂。</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022221" data-ratio="0.2361111111111111" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 637px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8SmcbXsviaYUcUVbUFBdicRMU6bhVSQnr1ichoQ6lycCN4mBLiaibKjnRK9sA/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></span></p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-conte