ng: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">如果你真实面试被拷打，希望对面试进行深度挖掘。解决面试中遇到的疑惑。</span><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">我们也会</span><strong style="outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(48, 79, 254);">对你真实的面试记录进行复盘</strong><span style="outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">。</span></span></span></p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"></span></span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"></span></span></figure><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022224" data-ratio="1.2703703703703704" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 25px;margin-left: auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8SsYdzGh5ee2Q6psEnLWvdyvWtPRRxPTbBOaibPAxdIynyibz2pibyaoquA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;font-family: Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;">目前训练营已经沉淀了很多同学新鲜出炉的大厂面经，这里的每一份面经都是可以学习的资料，因为每一份面经，导师们都针对同学面试回答做了评论和解析，会补充怎样答会更好，又或者需要去看哪些资料进一步学习。</span></figure><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022222" data-ratio="0.5518518518518518" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 25px;margin-left: auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8SyibTJENnXyDX1TQkaYKINibmBk01CL1klvax3tYdWqyaKv5dS26q2TFA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></figure><h3 data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 15px;outline: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 20px;color: black;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(65, 105, 225);"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100022226" data-ratio="1.123574144486692" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1052" style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;caret-color: transparent;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/J0g14CUwaZfTBeVIEa8TrgMs4Hw4OEiba1icZGNHKJPSErVIu81jCbSb2icgxhFwUoQ3Ja7FERQaicNkxfA6piarPGw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></span></h3><h3 data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 15px;outline: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 20px;color: black;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(65, 105, 225);">2. 有竞争力的大厂项目</span></h3><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding-top: 1em;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">我们训练营的</span><strong style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(48, 79, 254);">项目是大厂的真实项目</strong>，<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">是某位大厂程序员晋升答辩用的项目，我们经过改造后，作为训练营的项目，所以项目的立意是站的住的，</span><strong style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(48, 79, 254);">拿晋升的项目，给你们用来面试，妥妥地降维打击</strong>。</p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding-top: 1em;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">我们会从项目设计、架构设计、难点挖掘给大家讲解，这样的项目有数据支撑并经过生产验证，知道哪里有问题，哪里可优化，在面试时也会比较有优势。同时</span><strong style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(48, 79, 254);">针对项目的简历描述和面试问题</strong>，<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">我们都帮你整理好的了。</span></p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022223" data-ratio="1.1722222222222223" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 25px;margin-left: auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8SVZuTWrqI8Mt8Mdc2p8icyD4gAy5shD8fWU9fVKha6t05bibUsrTe4Qaw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></figure><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding-top: 1em;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">根据学员的反馈，训练营的项目是能让面试官感兴趣的，</span><strong style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(48, 79, 254);">一个能引起面试官感兴趣的项目，在面试是很加分的，你想想面试的时常通常都是固定的，如果有 60-70% 时间都在问项目，那么是不是八股文就问的少了，这样面试的难度相比全程都在挖八股文就降低了很多</strong>。</p><figure data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022225" data-ratio="0.2953703703703704" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 25px;margin-left: auto;outline: 0px;display: block;border-radius: 4px;visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/J0g14CUwaZclfA5G5lqv2EZ0gdZOtT8Scv8PqKPic08sfHln3HQS1VGgibVOnIsCkdia7xeqHa5XS3Wb25HlBokaw/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1&amp;tp=webp"></figure><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding: 16px 10px 8px;outline: 0px;text-indent: 0em;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0.02em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;text-indent: 0em;">我们项目的问题都帮大家准备好的了，面试可以完全不慌的！有黑马同学反馈我们的项目很顶，在面试中取到了很关键的作用！</span></p><p data-tool="mdnice编辑器" style="padding-top: 1em;padding-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022230" data-ratio="0.7722222222222223" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;w