 style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"></span></p><p style="margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">最重要的是，</span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;">求职面试也会成为加分项</span></strong></span><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">，自己动手写过操作系统，真有“飘”的资本，简历自然脱颖而出。</span></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 254, 213);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100022165" data-ratio="1.0157407407407408" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/VyxCxUCalFMGAhDfU3gh23NdpBcoSwhl481Wbzc172UMhFWD93eicB0zO4fKjbOkqELvnWlnEoHiaibuqeLIYHEDQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;font-size: 11pt;color: rgb(73, 73, 73);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;">扫码免费试读👆</span></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 29.3333px;font-size: 11pt;color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><br></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;font-size: 1