，再带你基于设计理解去动手实现；然后与 Linux内核的实现做前后对比。既能边学边练，又能帮你从“上帝视角”审视 Linux 内核。</span></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 11pt;color: rgb(73, 73, 73);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 11pt;color: rgb(73, 73, 73);line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100022159" data-ratio="0.7638888888888888" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" height="auto" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;" width="1280" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KyXfCrME6UKfiacS5H0RXruiacZfcCfMGuJeYFArzoxFicqejLchxNr2km0v5gDYQaKhThb4l7YxoqKU2WEvMB1pw/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 11pt;color: rgb(73, 73, 73);line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0pt 8px;outline: 0px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft